            "question": "How is this different from Medicare Advantage?",
            "answer": "PACE covers all Medicare and Medicaid services plus additional long-term care services like adult day programs and care coordination. Unlike Medicare Advantage, PACE participants never pay deductibles or co-pays for any covered services, and care is managed by one interdisciplinary team."
