        "name": "Kentucky Family Caregiver Program (Grandparents Raising Grandchildren)",
        "shortName": "Grandparent Caregiver Program",
        "tagline": "If you're raising your grandchild, Kentucky provides support services and grants for clothing, school supplies, and respite care.",
