        "id": "south-dakota-medicare-savings-programs",
        "name": "Medicare Savings Programs (QMB, SLMB, QI)",
        "shortName": "Medicare Savings Programs",
        "tagline": "If your parent's Medicare premiums and medical bills are overwhelming, these programs can pay $2,200+ annually in Medicare costs.",
